# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:25
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_d7391ca9:

    # "We walk until the sun begins to set and it's time to set up camp once again."
    "Caminhamos até o sol começar a pôr-se e chegar a hora de montar acampamento mais uma vez."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:28
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_6347fb4c:

    # mc "You say you are from another world, where there is another me?"
    mc "Dizes que és de outro mundo, onde existe outra versão de mim?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:29
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_ba87bb2f:

    # pc "Yeah, I am."
    pc "Sim, sou."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:30
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_2aa5ee09:

    # mc "What is she like? Is she a dancer as well?"
    mc "Como é ela? Também é bailarina?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:31
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_74677430:

    # pc "She is, actually. She loves to dance."
    pc "Na verdade, é. Adora dançar."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:32
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_b815dc04:

    # pc "She's very sweet and kind and always trying to please."
    pc "É muito doce e gentil e está sempre a tentar agradar."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:33
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_9ee66c04:

    # pc "She's a little too worried about pleasing everybody else, and doing what everybody else wants her to do..."
    pc "Preocupa-se um pouco demais em agradar a toda a gente e em fazer o que os outros querem que ela faça..."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:34
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_70ebbfb3:

    # pc "... instead of focusing on what she wants to do."
    pc "... em vez de se concentrar no que ela própria quer fazer."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:36
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_8eb4e936:

    # mc "Hm, that is not like me at all."
    mc "Hum, isso não é nada a meu estilo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:37
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_2c7a1ece:

    # mc "I always do what I want to do. I am free. Nobody tells Mi-Cha what to do... unless I want them to."
    mc "Eu faço sempre o que quero. Sou livre. Ninguém diz à Mi-Cha o que fazer... a menos que eu queira que o façam."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:39
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_42ed4bba:

    # mc "You have to help this other me see that. She is free to do whatever she wants."
    mc "Tens de ajudar esta outra versão de mim a perceber isso. Ela é livre para fazer o que quiser."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:40
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_078d69a7:

    # pc "I've been trying."
    pc "Tenho tentado."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:44
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_35550ef3:

    # cw "I lost my freedom for a long time. It's an awful feeling."
    cw "Perdi a minha liberdade durante muito tempo. É uma sensação horrível."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:45
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_2d600ef3:

    # cw "Everybody should be free to make their own decisions and do what they want with their lives."
    cw "Todos deviam ser livres para tomar as suas próprias decisões e fazer o que querem com as suas vidas."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:46
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_fcf340b6:

    # mc "I agree."
    mc "Concordo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:49
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_45de856f:

    # sg "Why would you care what anybody else thinks? They aren't living your life."
    sg "Porque te importarias com o que os outros pensam? Eles não estão a viver a tua vida."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:50
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_8ef70686:

    # sg "Just live it however makes you the happiest, I think."
    sg "Acho que deves simplesmente vivê-la da forma que te fizer mais feliz."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:51
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_7db64ce6:

    # sg "You only get one, and it's not very long."
    sg "Só tens uma, e não é muito longa."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:52
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_fcf340b6_1:

    # mc "I agree."
    mc "Concordo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:54
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_a52521e6:

    # gg "It's important to be whoever you feel like you are meant to be, and nobody else can decide that for you."
    gg "É importante seres quem sentes que estás destinada a ser, e mais ninguém pode decidir isso por ti."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:55
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_fcf340b6_2:

    # mc "I agree."
    mc "Concordo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:57
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_54bfdc0f:

    # bn "Sometimes it's difficult to know how to act, and guidance is necessary."
    bn "Às vezes é difícil saber como agir, e é necessária orientação."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:58
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_d671023b:

    # bn "But in the end, everybody should be free to make their own decisions."
    bn "Mas, no final, todos devem ser livres para tomar as suas próprias decisões."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:59
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_fcf340b6_3:

    # mc "I agree."
    mc "Concordo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:62
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_4387a8df:

    # sst "Freedom is the most important thing in the world."
    sst "A liberdade é a coisa mais importante do mundo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:63
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_aa965ea9:

    # sst "Nobody should be allowed to make decisions for you or control your fate!"
    sst "Ninguém deve ter permissão para tomar decisões por ti ou controlar o teu destino!"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:64
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_fcf340b6_4:

    # mc "I agree."
    mc "Concordo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:67
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_da8c9804:

    # rb "Nobody can tell Reba what to do!"
    rb "Ninguém pode dizer à Reba o que fazer!"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:68
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_6ac871f9:

    # rb "I'm gonna do whatever the heck I want to, I promise you that!"
    rb "Vou fazer o que bem me apetecer, prometo-te isso!"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:69
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_61a2b50c:

    # mc "That is a good way to live."
    mc "Essa é uma boa maneira de viver."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:71
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_5706ecf8:

    # mc "I will help you get back to her so that you can help her."
    mc "Vou ajudar-te a voltar para junto dela para que possas ajudá-la."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:72
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_124c4acc:

    # pc "Thanks Mi-Cha. It's definitely nice having you around."
    pc "Obrigado, Mi-Cha. É definitivamente bom ter-te por perto."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:73
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_a9a280cd:

    # mc "I am getting tired now. I think I will try to sleep."
    mc "Estou a ficar cansado agora. Acho que vou tentar dormir."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:74
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_d5f58427:

    # pc "Good idea. We should keep a watch overnight though. I can take first watch."
    pc "Boa ideia. Mas devemos ficar de vigia durante a noite. Eu posso ficar com a primeira vigia."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:77
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_d0ff659c:

    # sst "Then I will take second."
    sst "Depois, eu fico com a segunda."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:80
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_fd391d92:

    # rb "Then I will take second."
    rb "Depois, eu fico com a segunda."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:83
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_fa5c2825:

    # cw "Then I will take second."
    cw "Depois, eu fico com a segunda."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:86
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_9a2d0f32:

    # sg "Then me."
    sg "Depois, eu."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:89
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_f73f5a01:

    # bn "And I'll be next."
    bn "E eu sou o próximo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:92
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_ad230cd5:

    # gg "And I'll take the next one."
    gg "E eu fico com a seguinte."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:93
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_80ca8121:

    # mc "This is a good idea. I will do the last watch then."
    mc "É uma boa ideia. Então, eu fico com a última vigia."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:99
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_0466c0c7:

    # mc "This is fun. Travelling, talking, sleeping next to the fire."
    mc "Isto é divertido. Viajar, conversar, dormir junto à fogueira."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:100
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_2ee6cb68:

    # pc "Yeah, it is. If it wasn't for the bandits and the monsters, this place would be pretty nice."
    pc "Sim, é mesmo. Se não fossem os bandidos e os monstros, este lugar seria bastante agradável."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:101
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_68957625:

    # mc "Yes, that is true. I hope it stays peaceful like this."
    mc "Sim, é verdade. Espero que continue assim tão tranquilo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:104
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_98dcde50:

    # mc "Good night [pcname]. I am glad that we met."
    mc "Boa noite [pcname]. Fico contente por nos termos conhecido."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:105
translate portuguese u19a2s7a_eede79c7:

    # pc "Me too. Good night, Mi-Cha."
    pc "Eu também. Boa noite, Mi-Cha."

